# Online Winter Writing Sessions [Online, 17/01/2025-21/02/2025]

**Date:** Friday, January 17 2025 - Friday, February 21 2025—6 sessions on consecutive Friday mornings

**Time:** 9:30 AM to 12:30 PM

**Location:** Online on Zoom

Weekly Teams/Zoom sessions to work on your own writing individually, but with company (approaching writing as a collective endeavour can help hold us to account!)

Planned format for each session:
- Brief kick-off with writing tips presented by a different senior scholar each week.
- Share writing goals for the session in small breakout groups.
- Write (mics off) for 40 min, 10 min social break - repeat 3 times.

Organized and hosted by Wendy Kilminster, Lorenzo Maulini, Jadwiga Supryn from Säid Business School. If interested in joining, please email us at <londonqualitativecommunity@gmail.com>. 
